                        "meta": {
                            "course-unit-read": "<h3 data-fontsize=\"24\" data-lineheight=\"26\">What key activities do we need to run our business model?</h3>\r\nTo implement a business model a company needs to perform a number of key activities. It may perform these activities itself or get them done through a network of partners.",
                            "course-unit-read-more": "<h3 data-fontsize=\"24\" data-lineheight=\"26\">Key questions to answer:</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n \t<li> What are the main activities we operate to run our business model?</li>\r\n \t<li>On which key resources do they rely?</li>\r\n \t<li> To which value propositions, channels or relationships do they contribute?</li>\r\n</ul>",
